When it comes to family birthdays and special occasions, you don’t have to spend a fortune to make aunties, uncles, grannies, and grandpas feels special. Assist the kids in making these two fun crafty gift ideas, which double as wonderful sentimental gifts for loved ones. This is a wonderful sensory exercise for your little one with the repetitive pincer-grip practice for little hands, and a great gift. Ice-cream sticks offer many wonderful arts and crafts possibilities, so they’re always a great item to keep in your craft box. 